      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MARISSA VELLA (2) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at this track over 520m behind Extreme Machine (31.19) in a Maiden. Placed at her previous run. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Has ability and is a key runner. CONFUSION REIGNS (4) jumped cleanly and went straight to the lead, holding on for a place when second (30.24) at this track in a Maiden over 520m. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Expecting another good run. LORETTA KEEPING (5) shows ability but remains a maiden after six starts. Was in the placings again last time finishing second (30.18) at Richmond. Bold showing expected. SHE'S MAYHEM (1) is by Fernando Bale out of Ravishing In Red making debut. Gets every chance from the inside draw. Can feature with the right run.",
